title: DDFP 490: Week 2 recap, 'Dead or Alive' & Ike's Corner Corner
itunes:title: DDFP 490: Week 2 recap, 'Dead or Alive' & Ike's Corner Corner
description:
Shek is joined by Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew to discuss the status of "Exotic Smash Mouth" in Tennessee, the Seahawks' playoff chances and the early success of Carson Wentz. Then, the guys break down the best wins and worst losses from Week 2, highlighting the Vikings' win and the Redskins' loss. Also, the guys play a game of 'Dead or Alive' and Ike Taylor breaks down Trae Waynes' performance against the Packers in his new segment, "Ike's Corner Corner." Plus, in this week's "Time Machine Football," the guys review the 2003 Week 12 game between the Patriots and Texans in anticipation of Thursday Night Football.
